ta]] as Razia (Episode 787)\n* [[Anjali Abrol]] as Aditi Mishra (Episode 556) / Maya (Episode 736) / Piya (Episode 946) / Janvi (Episode 1127) / Keerti (Episode 1185) / Dr. Vasudha (Episode 1281) / Nivedita (Episode 1354) / Shikha (Episode 1463)\n* [[Ali Hassan (actor) | Ali Hassan]] as Ravi (Episode 471) / Episode 882 / Pankaj (Episode 1128) / Dr. Deepak (Episode 1468) / Sriram (Episode 1797)\n* [[Shakti Anand]] as Bharat Gupta (Episode 936) / Suraj Pratap  Singh (Episode 2158)<ref name=\"auto\">{{cite web|url=https://news.abplive.com/entertainment/television/savdhaan-india-shakti-anand-wife-sai-deodhar-to-reunite-onscreen-after-10-years-834415|title=Savdhaan India: Shakti Anand & wife Sai Deodhar to REUNITE onscreen after 10 years!|date=2017-07-03|website= ABP Live Dot Com|language=en|access-date=2020-01-24}}</ref>\n* [[Sai Deodhar]] as Sunaina Suraj Pratap Singh<ref name=\"auto\"/> (Episode 2158)\n* [[Aman Verma (actor) | Aman Verma]] as Inspector Rajendra Mishra (Episode 1065) / Mahesh (Episode 2162)\n* [[Nausheen Ali Sardar]] as Chandni<ref>{{cite web|url=https://m.timesofindia.com/tv/news/hindi/Nausheen-Ali-Sardaar-Anuj-Sharma-in-Savdhaan-India/articleshow/34483530.cms|title=Nausheen Ali Sardaar & Anuj Sharma in Savdhaan India|date=2014-05-01|website= Times Of India Dot Com|language=en|access-date=2020-03-04}}</ref> (Episode 673)\n* [[Rucha Gujarathi]] as Jayshree Shah (Episode 279)\n* [[Amrapali Gupta]] as Jyoti (Episode 90)\n* [[Shital Thakkar]] as Rashmi (Episode 682) / Shweta (Episode 862)\n* [[Sumana Das]] as Pratima (Episode 22)\n* [[Falaq Naaz]] as Manisha (Episode 36) / Rehana Hussain <ref>{{cite web|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/tv/news/hindi/Falaq-Naaz-in-Sunil-Agnihotris-Savdhaan-India/articleshow/18555126.cms |title=Falaq Naaz in Sunil Agnihotri's Savdhaan India|date=2013-02-18|website= Times Of India Dot Com|language=en|access-date=2020-03-04}}</ref> (Episode 201) / Naina <ref>{{cite web|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/tv/news/hindi/Rushad-Rana-Falaq-Naaz-in-Savdhaan-India/articleshow/19428248.cms|title=Rushad Rana & Falaq Naaz in Savdhaan India|date=2013-04-07|website= Times Of India Dot Com|language=en|access-date=2020-03-04}}</ref> (Episode 251) / Gauri (Episode 297)\n* [[Aastha Chaudhary]] as Geeta Joshi (Episode 2) / Priya Ajay Mishra (Episode 169)\n* [[Varun Badola]] as Inspector Varun<ref>{{cite web|url=https://m.timesofindia.com/tv/news/hindi/Varun-Badola-to-feature-in-Savdhaan-India/articleshow/21270634.cms|title=Varun Badola to feature in Savdhaan India|date=2013-07-23|website= Times Of India Dot Com|language=en|access-date=2020-03-04}}</ref> (Episode 384)\n* [[Mahhi Vij]] as Dr. Anju<ref>{{cite web|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/tv/news/hindi/Mahhi-Vij-roped-in-for-Savdhan-India/articleshow/16254697.cms|title=Mahhi Vij roped in for Savdhan India|date=2012-09-04|website= Times Of India Dot Com|language=en|access-date=2020-03-04}}</ref> (Episode 40) / Reha (Episode 1 - Episode 5)\n* [[Adaa Khan]] as Sneha Mulle / Pooja Saxena (Episode 425) / Malti Anmol Shah (Episode 1118)\n* [[Chaitanya Choudhury]] as Captain Vikram (Episode 804)\n* [[Hrishikesh Pandey]] as Inspector Surendra (Episode 2028)\n* [[Dalljiet Kaur]] as Shruti (Episode 31 - Episode 35)\n* [[Vikram Singh Chauhan]] as Gautam (Episode 653) / Arun (Episode 797)\n* [[Chetan Hansraj]] as ACP Abhijeet (Episode 1118)\n* [[Aashish Kaul]] as Mani Bhushan (Episode 450) / Ramen Sharma (Episode 522) / Advocate Vinay Salaskar (Episode 616) / Varun Khanna (Episode 789) / Abhinav (Episode 841) / Aashish (Episode 1422) / Amit (Episode 1694) / Aashish (Episode 1742) / Lakshman Singh Shekhawat (Episode 1890) / Mr. Gupta (Episode 1983)\n* [[Manav Gohil]] as Danny<ref>{{cite web|url=http://archive.indianexpress.com/news/manav-gohil-turns-gangster-for-savdhaan-india/1140060/|title=Manav Gohil turns gangster for Savdhaan India|date=2013-07-12|website= Indian Express Dot Com|language=en|access-date=2020-03-04}}</ref> (Episode 350)\n* 